OL,5, Derek Draper, the author and former    
OL,6, political adviser, has died aged 56,   
OL,7, his wife Kate Garraway has said.       
OL,9,FDraper had been living with extreme    
OL,10,Fcomplications from Covid since         
OL,11,Fcontracting the disease in March 2020. 
OL,13,FTV presenter Garraway confirmed his    
OL,14,Fdeath in a statement posted on         
OL,15,FInstagram.                             
OL,17,F"I'm sad to have to tell you all that  
OL,18,Fmy darling husband Derek has passed    
OL,19,Faway," she wrote.                      
